<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About | FoodSpot</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>

<body>

    <%- include('partials/header_index') %>
    <%- include('partials/main_nav') %>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <section class="about-section">
        <h2 class="reach">ABOUT FOODSPOT</h2>
        <blockquote>
            "People who love to eat are always the best people." - Julia Child
        </blockquote>
        <div class="intro">
            At FoodSpot, our passion is to deliver delicious meals right to your doorstep. Built on ambition, trust, and hard work, we've crafted a unique online food delivery experience just for you.
        </div>

        <div class="team-intro">
            <div class="team-picture">
                <img width="200px" height="200px" src="./Assets/images/ceo.jpg">
            </div>
            <div class="team-detail">
                <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                <p>Bringing the world's cuisines to your table with just a click. Dive into our journey and experience the magic of online food delivery.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="team-intro">
            <div class="team-picture">
                <img width="200px" height="200px" src="./Assets/images/team.jpg">
            </div>
            <div class="team-detail">
                <h3>Our Passionate Team</h3>
                <p>Meet the FoodSpot Family - a group of 5 dedicated professionals who have been setting standards in the online food delivery industry since 2022.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="team-intro">
            <div class="team-picture">
                <img width="200px" height="200px" src="./Assets/images/history.jpg">
            </div>
            <div class="team-detail">
                <h3>Our Journey</h3>
                <p>From a handful of 5 food enthusiasts with a vision, to the leading force in online food delivery. FoodSpot's story is one of passion, innovation, and culinary delights.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/bottom_nav') %>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <!-- Custom Styles -->
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .about-section {
            padding: 50px;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .reach {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .intro {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        blockquote {
            font-style: italic;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #333;
            color: #777;
        }

        .team-intro {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .team-detail h3 {
            color: #444;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .team-detail p {
            color: #777;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .team-picture img {
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 3px solid #333;
        }
    </style>
</body>

</html>
